---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lastUpdated = "July 9, 2026";
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Cornfed Bucks collects, uses, and protects visitor information.">
  <section class="legal">
    <div class="wrap legal__inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy Policy</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how Cornfed Bucks ("we," "us," "our," or "Cornfed Bucks") collects,
        uses, and protects information when you visit cornfedbucks.com (the "Site"). By using the Site,
        you agree to the practices described here.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information in a few limited ways:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Newsletter signup information.</strong> If you subscribe to The Monday Morning Report,
          we collect the email address you provide through our newsletter signup form. Newsletter
          delivery and subscriber management is handled by our email service provider, beehiiv. Their
          use of your information is governed by their own privacy policy.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Analytics data.</strong> We use website analytics (including Cloudflare Analytics and,
          where enabled, Google Search Console) to understand aggregate traffic patterns — such as which
          pages are visited, general geographic region, device type, and referral source. This data is
          used in aggregate and is not used to personally identify individual visitors.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cookies.</strong> The Site and its third-party providers (such as beehiiv and Amazon
          Associates) may use cookies or similar technologies to support core functionality, remember
          preferences, and track affiliate referrals. You can disable cookies through your browser
          settings, though some site features may not function as intended if you do.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>To send the Monday Morning Report newsletter to subscribers who opt in.</li>
        <li>To understand how visitors use the Site, so we can improve content and site performance.</li>
        <li>To track affiliate referrals, so we can earn commissions on qualifying purchases made through our links.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

      <h2>Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>
        Cornfed Bucks participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program and may participate in
        other affiliate programs. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, the retailer's
        own tracking cookie records the referral, and we may earn a commission at no additional cost to
        you. See our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</a> for more detail.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p>We rely on the following third-party services, each with its own privacy practices:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>beehiiv</strong> — newsletter hosting and email delivery.</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon Associates</strong> — affiliate link tracking and commissions.</li>
        <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — site hosting, content delivery, and analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        The Site is not directed at children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal
        information from children under 13.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Choices</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You can unsubscribe from the newsletter at any time using the link in any email we send.</li>
        <li>You can disable cookies in your browser at any time.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an
        updated "Last updated" date.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this Privacy Policy can be directed to <a href="mailto:nick@cornfedbucks.com">nick@cornfedbucks.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal { padding: 3.5rem 0 5rem; }
  .legal__inner { max-width: 680px; }
  .legal h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.6rem);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  .legal .updated {
    font-family: var(--font-tag);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal h2 {
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }
  .legal p, .legal li {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .legal ul { padding-left: 1.3rem; }
  .legal li { margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
</style>
